  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/3d35a6ad68f88f384c90d1dd68440dcc.avif?t=1727511221\" width=640 height=172 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>ENTER THE WORLD OF HEAVY METAL MUSIC!<br><br>Unleash your inner metalhead spirit with Rhythmetallic, a heavy metal music rhythm game featuring a growing collection of epic metal music with classic tap tap style gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.mp4?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><strong>CLASSIC GAMEPLAY</strong><br>No unnecessary gestures or mechanics. Just feel the rhythm and be precise when tapping the notes. Headbang and play along the music as if you are the guitar hero of a heavy metal band!<br><br><strong>MUSIC</strong><br>With 40+ songs (another 70+ songs if you own the DLC) across different metal genres such as heavy metal, thrash metal, melodic death metal, black metal, power metal and djent), there must be songs that are sure to satisfy your metal hunger.<br><br><strong>COMPETE</strong><br>Hone your skills and work you way to the top of the global leaderboard to show that you are the real rhythm game master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/b7190376e080bf97c85255e8527629af.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/b7190376e080bf97c85255e8527629af.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/b7190376e080bf97c85255e8527629af.mp4?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/66a97858e1a288592e1b6552b1b2d8bc.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/66a97858e1a288592e1b6552b1b2d8bc.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/66a97858e1a288592e1b6552b1b2d8bc.mp4?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/903e80215692a21193ff2ab7a7d5782f.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/903e80215692a21193ff2ab7a7d5782f.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/903e80215692a21193ff2ab7a7d5782f.mp4?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join us to the heavy metal world to tap and headbang your way through epic metal tracks!",
  "about_the_game": "ENTER THE WORLD OF HEAVY METAL MUSIC!<br><br>Unleash your inner metalhead spirit with Rhythmetallic, a heavy metal music rhythm game featuring a growing collection of epic metal music with classic tap tap style gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/d53b806bccc3aeb768acedd1428955b3.mp4?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><strong>CLASSIC GAMEPLAY</strong><br>No unnecessary gestures or mechanics. Just feel the rhythm and be precise when tapping the notes. Headbang and play along the music as if you are the guitar hero of a heavy metal band!<br><br><strong>MUSIC</strong><br>With 40+ songs (another 70+ songs if you own the DLC) across different metal genres such as heavy metal, thrash metal, melodic death metal, black metal, power metal and djent), there must be songs that are sure to satisfy your metal hunger.<br><br><strong>COMPETE</strong><br>Hone your skills and work you way to the top of the global leaderboard to show that you are the real rhythm game master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/b7190376e080bf97c85255e8527629af.poster.avif?t=1727511221\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673620/extras/b7190376e080bf97c85255e8527629af.webm?t=1727511221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><